description:
In this Sabbath School Lesson, we will study Romans 10:4 where Paul says that “Christ is the end of the law.” Did Paul meanthat we no longer have to keep God’s Ten Commandments?

Lesson Guide: https://www.prophesyagain.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Is-Jesus-Christ-The-End-Of-The-Law.pdf
